reviewText: I like each episode it broke 9 years ago
The VHS was in good condition and pleased my grandson whose other copy was defective.  Shipping was as promised.

At the Movies is really good but this tape is worth the price for Reptar on Ice alone. Operatic treatment of skating dinosaur show is hysterical; my husband and I sing it around the house all the time. Kids love all Rugrats but the best ones are for grown-ups too.
